{"tid":624191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律師會引述京官：中國非一黨專政","createTime":"2018-04-10T15:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T16:59:56.000Z","uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d65e6a188af81c5e458e2a37a90711a39480f92c","tid":624191,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】律師會訪問北京，分別與港澳辦副主任黃柳權及基本法委員會主任沈春耀會面。會長蘇紹聰引述黃柳權指，中國實行多黨合作制，說反對一黨專政的人違憲是存在誤解。 <br />\n<br />\n律師會會長蘇紹聰率團訪問北京，期間與港澳辦副主任黃柳權會面。<br />\n<br />\n雙方談到港大學者戴耀廷在台灣提出反專制運動成功後，香港及其他內地城市可以考慮獨立的言論，蘇紹聰引述黃柳權表示，言論自由在香港得到保障，但也有限制，界線是根據香港法律界定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，內地早前修憲確立共產黨的領導地位，蘇紹聰引述黃柳權表示，反對一黨專政的人違憲這個說法有誤解。<br />\n<br />\n訪京團又拜訪了基本法委員會主任沈春耀，表達律師會對一地兩檢的憂慮。蘇紹聰指，對方回應表示人大經過嚴謹考慮後作出決定，並非一個馬虎決定，亦不會做出一些損害一國兩制的行為。"},{"pid":"eb6d1a209fc4cde7a0292a1af944d84b9200d05c","tid":624191,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"55😂"},{"pid":"5b79492ba63f094e6100bd92ad2c05a185750f70","tid":624191,"uid":15075,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:27:13.000Z","msg":"64無死過人"},{"pid":"0bfd3fd8886fed1c056652ca304a0ebdb250fda4","tid":624191,"uid":117965,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:28:13.000Z","msg":"中國有害氣體無害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b40121fe5664fd04105c197dcceb29d4376f4df0","tid":624191,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"中國實行多黨合作制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他係咪黨"},{"pid":"d7ca4653b8a23f94727d9ec650fa839a5069eb22","tid":624191,"uid":6347,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:31:31.000Z","msg":"除左共產黨仲有扑頭黨同迷暈黨？"},{"pid":"ea15ff4fd155df51bbdbb7a4b085401559001a0b","tid":624191,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f25114aebb54258e2a12fa871ee2358da16c902","tid":624191,"uid":35221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b40121fe5664fd04105c197dcceb29d4376f4df0","tid":624191,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"中國實行多黨合作制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他係咪黨"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:33:45.000Z","msg":"中華人民共和國係行<strong><ins>中國共產黨領導的多黨合作和政治協商制度</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n執政黨：<br />\n中國共產黨<br />\n<br />\n參政黨：<br />\n中國國民黨革命委員會<br />\n中國民主同盟<br />\n中國民主建國會<br />\n中國民主促進會<br />\n中國農工民主黨<br />\n中國致公黨<br />\n九三學社<br />\n台灣民主自治同盟"},{"pid":"ddeb63d14d2fa2f5f60cff96596c543dbbfea843","tid":624191,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"律師會呢個講法好毒<br />\n黃柳權只係港澳辦副主任,連人大都唔係<br />\n<br />\n姐係任何京官都可以釋法"},{"pid":"fc4ccb3eefba947650419a6fcde7cc48a7096188","tid":624191,"uid":35221,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ddeb63d14d2fa2f5f60cff96596c543dbbfea843","tid":624191,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"律師會呢個講法好毒<br />\n黃柳權只係港澳辦副主任,連人大都唔係<br />\n<br />\n姐係任何京官都可以釋法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"何君堯都做過律師會會長，知咩事"},{"pid":"fa534e95d6dd8b4e25e3445c4e0263b8ff0a4aa3","tid":624191,"uid":89063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T15:50:04.000Z","msg":"是非完全顛倒<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/234919_9f5ce2ef4cdcb3d84aaf29cbe4171711.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F234919_9f5ce2ef4cdcb3d84aaf29cbe4171711.png&h=e18dc732&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/234920_321e425b5f309bbc069cd8247b5079ce.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F234920_321e425b5f309bbc